INSERT INTO messages VALUES (37,17,1,30,5,'Racer X','As do I...','Much better layout.\r\nNot just for the boards, but for the entire game. The \'recent messages\' thing is great! Character creation is just what SotF needed. This is so much faster loading too! My equipment screen used to take me 5 minutes (literally) to load in the original!\r\nThe only thing I could suggest, would be a few more \"pre-war scrap heaps\" and the likes, for our scavenging friends.','2001-05-07 19:02:01');
