INSERT INTO messages VALUES (43,18,1,38,1,'Rizen','thought about it','i thought about it, but i\'ve been thinking that things like theft should be pvp. this game is all about beating the other players, not beating the npcs...you see what i mean?','2001-05-07 20:02:32');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (44,19,3,33,6,'Kurtillius','Don\'t worry!','I\'m heading over to the Ninth Gate tavern to tell all the deserters to get back, now that our beloved Quid is back again! It\'ll be exciting in no time again!','2001-05-07 20:04:41');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (45,29,2,32,6,'Kurtillius','Except with more fighting.','Hence, the need for a bar brawls board. Of course, Fradam would always be a numchkin, and cheat to win.\r\n\r\n*Fradam picks Kurt up, and throws him onto a table. Kurt groans in pain.*\r\n\r\n((He\'d always make me do things like that!))\r\n\r\n*Fradam gestures two of his friends over, and all three body slam Kurt, and hit him with chairs. This goes on for 4 paragraphs, as Fradam is God, and can control EVERYONE*\r\n\r\nSee, that\'s why I had to make the official Quidnunc rules of fighting, which we all agreed to follow.','2001-05-07 20:07:55');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (46,40,3,42,5,'Racer X','I think...','Not being in Quid is close enough to an affinity, I guess. But, is there more than one place that won\'t allow Quidders?','2001-05-07 20:08:52');
