INSERT INTO messages VALUES (49,49,1,0,7,'Cymru Ddreig','Frailty','I got this message when fighting:\r\n\r\nthe hawk gashed Cymru Ddreig, and Cymru Ddreig sustained additional injuries due to frailty.\r\nthe hawk barely hit Cymru Ddreig, and Cymru Ddreig sustained additional injuries due to frailty.\r\nthe hawk damaged Cymru Ddreig, and Cymru Ddreig sustained additional injuries due to frailty.\r\nCymru Ddreig gashed the hawk.\r\nYou were unable to kill the hawk.\r\n\r\nhow can i be frail? my age sez 22, and i can\'t see anything else that would change it.\r\n','2001-05-07 20:19:26');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (50,18,1,43,5,'Racer X','I do..','But realistically, in the dE world, you can steal from vendors in towns.. but you could also attack them.. with a little backlash!\r\nBut still, stealing from vendors would help a player win..','2001-05-07 20:42:43');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (51,29,2,47,8,'randomsyllable','rules','There are none?\r\n\r\ncourtesy is expected, but not required. however, no one like an asshole','2001-05-07 21:37:30');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (52,52,1,0,8,'randomsyllable','New stuff','Two new suggestions:\r\n\r\n1) If we are eventually going to implement NPC\'s that wander around, how about expanding the amenities to include \"name\" locations. Something like a trade depot run by Hagi Christ(i?) or a Power/Raider controlled town with different affinity sets. or at least more extreme ones.\r\n\r\n2) There needs to be stonger animals. Once I can kill Crimson terrors in a single blow barehanded, there is little that can actively take me out besides players. there needs to be \"You have contracted a plague\" or \"You have met the wrong end of a BattleBot (forget the real name)\" things that *will* kill you that aren\'t rads or human controlled.','2001-05-07 21:52:11');
