INSERT INTO messages VALUES (218,211,5,214,1,'Rizen','help with that','fewer towns will have the kill reaction when the new beta gets released. i\'ve implemented a number of new reactions, therefore kill gets moved down the list of likelyhood.\r\n\r\nwe can move it further down the list of likelyhood if you guys can help me come up with other reactions to affinities.\r\n\r\nso far the affinities are these (as of beta 10):\r\nquidders\r\nmurderers\r\nthieves\r\ngunslingers (someone with gun equipped)\r\nmutants\r\nno afinity\r\n\r\nso far the reactions are these (as of beta 10):\r\nkill\r\nmaime\r\nshame\r\nfine\r\nno reaction\r\njail\r\njail and fine\r\njail and maime\r\nwarn\r\n\r\n\r\nif you can think of additional reactions, then that will lessen the chance of the kill reaction being assigned to a community.','2001-05-10 15:41:35');
