INSERT INTO messages VALUES (374,371,1,373,7,'Cymru Ddreig','Could you go one step further?','That seems lieka good idea, but why should people neccesarily be paid?  Blacksmiths would take apprentices to teach them a trade, and pay them for nothing but a portion of the price the things they made sold.  If you want to work, you need to gain the skills, so how about if you learn teh skills at the places, get paid very little and then when you make stuff with the skills, you can get better money?','2001-05-14 16:09:04');
