INSERT INTO messages VALUES (390,390,1,0,24,'MrSelfDestruct','Chemotherapy','As the undisputed heavyweight champion of cancer, I can honestly say: enough with the rads already. \r\n\r\nI\'m at 558 and counting, and I\'m really starting to believe that there is a pattern to them.  It looks like once a particular slide starts to happen, for better or for worse, it stays that way for a long time.  \r\n\r\nTake my Shielding score for example.  At one time it was a pretty decent 5, but then I \"contracted\" a couple rads that took it to -2, and now, many moons later, it is still plummeting.  Let\'s just say that once it hits -30, you \"feel a little strange\" every single time you take a step.  No joke.  Every time.\r\n\r\nAnother one is Combat.  I was happy when it was 18, but now it\'s 48 and it just keeps going up.  \r\n\r\nThe sky\'s the limit, I guess.  I just wish there were WAY fewer of them, so that when you got one or two, it had a greater impact.','2001-05-14 17:52:38');
