INSERT INTO messages VALUES (414,371,1,395,4,'stroker ace','lets not forget','lets look at what your contemplating, on another level...this game is fun for certain reasons, a main one is the ways of generating funds we have now are from skills we would not normally use in everyday life...that is a good thing, it gives us the taste for adventure, something our own world desperatly lacks...while i like the idea of having a few new skills, such as limited ability to repair equipment, do not forget why we play this...if these things happen whats next, it opens the doors for too many BORING JOB possibilities...too many skills and the use of towns would become obsolete...whoever plays this game to produce funds by being a waiter/waitress in a tavern should be hit in the head with a brick, i mean come on people, were all SMARTER than that...the best idea IS ADVENTURE ADVENTURE ADVENTURE...Rizen hit the nail on the head when he integrated that into the taverns, and frankly i\'m dissapointed in all of us, including me in not taking further steps to blossom THOSE ideas...we have all been aiming at the wrong bullseye here, so no more talk about jobs we do in everyday life...I DARE ALL OF YOU TO COME UP WITH SOME ORIGINAL SWASH BUCKLIN, DUST EATIN, FALLIN OFF THE CHAIR, ONE HIT WONDERS...MAY SUVIVAL BE WITH YOU...ace out ','2001-05-14 22:46:56');
