INSERT INTO messages VALUES (449,443,1,443,1,'Rizen','all good ideas','however, the quests system that i\'ve implemented is VERY limited at this point. it is not meant to be a major function of the game. it has these limitations (some of which are self-imposed on purpose).\r\n\r\n1) quests can only be handed out and completed by the bartender.\r\n\r\n2) quests all involve retrieving one or more objects. (all objects must be of the same type.)\r\n\r\n3) rewards are all item based. therefore they can be money based as well because money is just an item with large quantity.\r\n\r\n4) quests cannot involve specific animals at specific locations as they are randomly generated and not tied directly to the map. this goes for npc events as well. eventually we may make animals and other npcs actually process as characters on the map, but for now they are generated on an as needed basis.\r\n','2001-05-15 15:26:09');
