INSERT INTO messages VALUES (587,558,1,585,5,'Racer X','I can answer one part...','There is almost always a chance of dying when you attack something... everything you do is based on a roll of dice, and the rabbit could get an extremely high roll, and you could get extrememly low.\r\nIE: You have a 7 combat, and we\'ll say a rabbit has 2. You roll all 1\'s, and end up with a 7. The rabbit rolls two 6\'s and ends up with 12. He then has a higher chance of hitting than you do.\r\nUnderstand?','2001-05-18 21:48:47');
