INSERT INTO messages VALUES (592,522,2,591,6,'Kurtillius','Oh, Fradam. Here.','Kurt reaches into his pocket, and pulls a cookie out of his pocket. He brushes the lint off.\r\n\r\n\"Here you go! Fetch!\"\r\n\r\nKurt throws the cookie across the room, hitting Dinsdale in the stomach, landing at his feet.\r\n\r\n\"There.\"\r\n\r\nKurt turns back to his drink.','2001-05-18 23:41:05');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (593,522,2,592,5,'Racer X','\"Hey.. Kurt...\"','\"What? No cookie for me?\"\r\n\r\n::<i>sits down beside Kurt and puts his hand on Kurt\'s shoulder</i>::\r\n\r\n\"Gimme a cookie, or get a shovel in the face!\"\r\n\r\n::<i>lifts up his shirt, revealing a rather large shovel taped to his stomach</i>::\r\n\r\n\"...I\'m not joking.\"','2001-05-18 23:55:47');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (594,522,2,593,6,'Kurtillius','\"Aaaaugh!!!!!!\"','\"Look out! He might just be crazy enough to do it! Don\'t worry, folks! I\'ll handle him! Run for your lives!\"\r\n\r\nKurt throws his drink in Racer\'s face, then dives off his stool, into Racer, sending them both tumbling to the ground.\r\n\r\n\"AAAAAAAAAIIIIIIIEEEEEEEEEE!!!!!!!!!!!!!\"\r\n\r\nKurt bites Racer\'s shin with all his strength, latching on.','2001-05-18 23:58:41');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (595,522,2,594,5,'Racer X','::Lifts up his shirt::','::and attempts to rip the shovel off of his stomach, but the shovel is taped too tightly and won\'t come off::\r\n\r\n\"Meh..I\'m gonna allow this...\"\r\n\r\n::keeps his eyes on Kurt, making sure that, as Kurt knaws at his shin, he makes no movements towards the groin::\r\n\r\n\"Just stay above the equator...\"\r\n','2001-05-19 00:03:22');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (596,522,2,595,6,'Kurtillius','Spits blood out','\"I\'m already below the equator, idiot! WAY below it!\"\r\n\r\nKurt gets up, and grabs a bottle of alcohol. We\'ll say it\'s brandy. He splashes it on Racer\'s torso and arms, and pulls out a match.\r\n\r\n\"Shovel this, bastard!\"\r\n\r\nKurt strikes the match, failing to see the alcohol he splashed on his hand. Kurt\'s hand bursts into flames, and, howling, Kurt dives down onto Racer, igniting the two in a big, flaming heap.','2001-05-19 00:08:53');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (597,522,2,596,5,'Racer X','::runs around blindly::','::<i>failing to notice that he happens to have fire resistant clothing, and the flames do nothing to him</i>::\r\n\r\n\"Ahh!! I\'m Flamey!\"\r\n\r\n::<i>realizing he has the pwoer of fire on his side, he runs around, hoping his running will cause something to happen::\r\n\r\n\"Bow before me, for I am your god!!\"','2001-05-19 00:12:44');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (598,522,2,597,6,'Kurtillius','\"Ouch.\"','Still on fire, Kurt climbs up to the bar, a resumes his seat.\r\n\r\n\"Quid? Water over here. Thanks.\r\n\r\nKurt coughs through the smoke billowing off of his clothes and pours the liquid onto his flaming hand, extinguishing the blaze. Oblivoius to the rest his body\'s flames, Kurt orders another round.\r\n\r\n\"Horses eat oats.\"\r\n\r\n((OOC- That\'s an inside joke.))','2001-05-19 00:15:43');
