INSERT INTO messages VALUES (644,644,1,0,1,'Rizen','Beta 13','SotF will be upgraded to beta 13 in a few minutes...Perhaps it\'s even being done as we speak. It represents a significant milestone in our journey to v2 as SotF2 is now feature complete.\r\n\r\nWhat this means:\r\n1) We\'ve now completed all of the features we set out to build at the start of this version.\r\n2) With the exception of bug fixes, there will be no changes of code between now and the release date.\r\n\r\n\r\nThis does not mean that we\'ve finished working on SotF permanently. It simply means we need to spend the next week and a half sweeping up the sawdust and polishing the silver so that it\'s ready to release to the public.\r\n\r\nAfter we launch, we\'ll start working on new features again, but our work on SotF will be far more limited as our focus will be diverted to our new game: Star Games\r\n','2001-05-20 17:23:38');
