INSERT INTO messages VALUES (647,522,2,624,6,'Kurtillius','OOC: He says....','That he\'s not going to reply to this post, ever. He says I can do whatever I want, and he won\'t reply. He got mad that he was so stupid, I guess.\r\n\r\nKurt begins pummeling Dins in the face, for Dins has chosen to stand like a statue. Kurt then grabs Dinsdale\'s collar, and drags him across the bar, sending all the drinks crashing to the floor. Kurt throws Dins onto a table, and Dins still makes no move to counter or defend himself. Kurt begins picking up chairs and stools, and smashing them over his prone form. Then, Kurt begins smashing bottle, and then picking up the shards of glass, and throwing them again. Kurt grabs Dinsdale\'s unresponsive form, and hefts him into the air.\r\n\r\n\"What\'s that? You refuse to defend yourself? Alright, Shoeboy.\"\r\n\r\nKurt slams Dinsdale against a wall, and holds him there. Kurt begins headbutting Dins, and shaking him. Dins does nothing, as stated earlier. Kurt lets go, and Dins slumps to the floor, where Kurt begins stomping on his groin. Kurt turns to Eeeegor.\r\n\r\n\"Hey Eeegs! Gimme that baton of yours! He\'s refusing to move a muscle!\"','2001-05-20 17:57:00');
