INSERT INTO messages VALUES (840,797,3,837,11,'Eeeegor','my thoughts','this over sotf1 quid.\r\n\r\nthe old quid over this.\r\n\r\nAs everyone else said, the sense of community was much stronger... and, also, to be in Quidnunc meant something onsite, it really did.  Here, it doesnt mean anything really to those non quidders.  Being in Quidnunc meant respect, the respect of the rest of the site.\r\n\r\nI think that bringing clans, and characters back to dE would do alot, and i mean ALOT!\r\n\r\nOn the matter of the Quid Stockpiles, sounds good to me.  How would it work? Like the old troubadour system?\r\n\r\nBishop, about those stories, yeah, i wanna here about noz in oz too.   Maybe if we\'re really good and eat our veggies we\'ll get a story about it ;)','2001-05-30 01:45:31');
