INSERT INTO messages VALUES (868,868,3,0,6,'Kurtillius','OOC: You know you\'re a....','I\'ve compiled this little test that you can take in the comfort of your own homes to see if you\'re a dE <b>Golden Oldie!</b> If you were really around in the dE Golden Ages, answer these questions:\r\n\r\nDo you own a copy of the original character sheet where certain shaded parts of the characters anatomy were visible?\r\n\r\nDo you have a copy of the original free PHB that you could download, before dE was published?\r\n\r\nDo you remember the famous Pieso \"Stupid Americans\" tirade?\r\n\r\nDid you put in your two cents on whether the PHB should be published?\r\n\r\nWere you there when the original Clutterspeak came out?\r\n\r\nHave you ever submitted anything before karma came about?\r\n\r\nDo you remember when the TROUBADOUR section only had 6 stories in it? \r\n\r\nDo you remember when the Wraiths weren\'t as large as the population of China?\r\n\r\nHave you seen the old CLANS listing, when it consisted only of Clan Name, Location, and Number of Members?\r\n\r\nHave you ever talked to Seth BEFORE he got bitter about dE and life in general?\r\n\r\nDo you know who Doomsday is?\r\n\r\nDid you take part in the original <i>\"help me i need a clan\"</i> Dinsdale thread back when he was \'BRETT_M\'? (This one is OLD)\r\n\r\nDo you know how to properly use the now gone skill ULTIMATE FIGHTING?\r\n\r\nDid you ever look in the revision history and see \"Added skills haggle, appraise, and broadcasting\" (Or something along those lines)?\r\n\r\nDid you take place in the original RACE TO QUID when karma first came out, and we all were going for it to get in first? (Doomsday won, I came in second, Pieso came in 3rd.)\r\n\r\nDo you remember the first time Eegs ever weilded the Godstick? (This is getting further away from the Golden Ages, but I couldn\'t help it.)\r\n\r\nHahah! That was fun! Feel free to add, if I missed anything!','2001-05-30 22:08:09');
