INSERT INTO messages VALUES (965,965,3,0,111,'Xanthii','Nine Lives','Xanthii brushes the golden streaked hair from her eyes and removes her brown cape, shaking the worst of the road dust just outside the doorstep. Putting it over her arm she steps inside and allows her eyes to adjust to the lighting. The feral pupils narrow to vertical slits, taking it all in.\r\n\r\nXanthii\'s face has a distinct feline look, pale tan with three tigerish strikes accenting her cheekbones, curving in toward her mouth. First glance often gives the impression that these markings are the product of henna tattooing rather than the soft thin fur that covers her and is her deadEarth reality.\r\n\r\nShe stands approximately 6ft in height (mostly with the benefit of the heels on her thigh high boots) and wears form fitting leather in the same shade as her cape. Her collar is studded and bears a painted brand.\r\n\r\nThe Number 9.\r\n\r\nHearing her name she searches the din for the source and finds Eeeegor. A slow smile curves on her full lips, revealing tiny white fanged incisors.\r\n\r\nHer voice is a low purr...\r\n\r\n\"Don\'t mind if I do. The trip has been long and I\'ve a lot to tell...\"','2001-06-03 08:10:24');
