INSERT INTO messages VALUES (972,931,5,931,4,'stroker ace','what happened','man was i tore up last night...i remember in the first version of SOTF message boards, attempting to write a couple of long piles of words and the game wouldnt accept it...if theres a limit to the number of lines you can have, i havent found it...is there?...so if not i could write a sotf short story on a subject of interest...such as one that only states the facts...only the names will be changed...its only interesting if people read it...nahh...as long as 1 person agrees with something i have said i did my job...unless you think your concience and morals does not play a part in the event of a nuclear war?...if you think about it good verses evil is not a new concept...why not be able to choose your characters disposition from the start?...that alone could dictate the course of many events...think about it...','2001-06-03 10:52:28');
