INSERT INTO messages VALUES (975,797,3,815,111,'Xanthii','OOC: One key difference','Now that I\'ve read through most of the messages, I can see one key difference between the two Quids that might be all the difference in the \"feel\" of each.\r\n\r\nWe used to think of Quid\'s Tavern as \"roleplay only\". There are other message boards for those who play sotf...it might help to keep the sotf game talk to one of them, rather than here... in an attempt to promote more freeform.\r\n\r\nOne reason a lot of us left was because there was so much focus on the sotf, that the hardcore roleplayers felt abandoned. Our only refuge was Quid\'s Tavern. When that was taken away, we had no reason to be here anymore.\r\n\r\nCo-existance is possible, but it\'s difficult to talk \"in character\" with other people talking \"turns\" and such. In the imortal words of The Offspring...\"Ya gotta keep em separated...\"\r\n\r\nAdvice? Change the name and make it RP only. Wehn you do that, it will become a \"place to be\" instead of a place to write.\r\n\r\nThat is the first step to recreating \"community.\"\r\n\r\nMy thoughts.\r\n\r\nXandra','2001-06-03 11:43:03');
