INSERT INTO messages VALUES (983,965,3,977,111,'Xanthii','Xanthii raises a brow','\"I\'ve never been known to be an entertainer, but you are free to listen.\"\r\n\r\nXanthii puts her cloak over the back of her chair and pulls it out to sit. Signaling for a drink, she murmers something to a barmaid and slips standards into her waiting hands. More than enough for several rounds. Crossing one long leg over the other she looks at her two companions.\r\n\r\nWaiting a moment in silence for the delivery of her drink, when it arrives, she takes it down in two swallows and gestures to keep them coming.\r\n\r\n\"A year ago, a man by the name of Marcus decided to renovate an old basement into a neighborhood tavern in Nawlin\'s. After much dealing with the owners of this building, he moved in and set up his business. Mysteriously...the owners disappeared.\r\n\r\n\"Time passed and he noticed odd things happening around him. Cellar doors that unlocked themselves, Windows that even bricks and mortar couldn\'t keep closed. His associate (and upstairs neighbor) Karma Leon, a mystic, told him there was a presence in his tavern. The presence guarded a gateway to the spiritual world.\r\n\r\n\"Of course, Marcus scoffed at such nonsense, but nonetheless, he jumped at shadows. He was, after all, a rather superstitious cajun-type and even with all his manly common sense, there was still a nagging feeling about the place. The feeling of being watched. He told me of this several times and jokingly called the entity, The GateKeeper.\r\n\r\n\"I thought it was an old bar joke, you knwo... something to be sniggered at, but none could deny the cold breezes that ran through the place, or the shifting shadows in the rafters that seemed to hang on every word of each patron.\r\n\r\nShe stops for a moment, taking another glass and downing it quickly. Wiping the corner of her mouth with a taloned thumb, she continues...\r\n\r\n\"One night I witnessed something that...up until then I thought was just...fantasy. One minute I was laughing and having a good time with the Krewe...and the next...\r\n\r\n\"The next I saw this...gate open up and swallow them whole. And there was nothing I could do about it...\"','2001-06-03 20:23:13');
