INSERT INTO messages VALUES (992,965,3,987,15,'Fradam','*pokes head around*','<i>Fradam turns his head around the Family\'s booth, to find the reacquainted friends seated and at a slight pause in conversation. His eyes slightly out of focus, Fradam stares straight at Eeegor\'s eyes.</i>\r\n\r\n\"Eeegor, you know as well as I do your tale will take less than a minute to tell -- you spend more time dressing yourself in the morning than you would telling Xanthii of your tale!\"\r\n\r\n<i>Fradam hiccuped, then laughed uproariously at his own joke, before turning back to a cookie he was eating that had a strange yellowish tinge to it, and continuing his murmurings.</i>\r\n\r\n\"Come now my precious... all for me...\"','2001-06-04 08:12:30');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (993,931,5,942,15,'Fradam','this should be interesting','it wasnt a fraud? try and justify \"negative plane and spending turns\". please, do.\r\n\r\nwhat you forget, that february was the month of non\'s. dado walked over everybody, and if you were a quidder, there wasnt much you could do, except join bishop hood.\r\n\r\nyou had as much chance of every other quidder that month of winning... virtually none. who cares if dado was murdered or whatnot on the day of the reset? if you werent sitting in the negative plane spending turns, dado would have slain you with ease before you had passed 2.5k turns. and you know it, since that\'s how all quidders were treated.\r\n\r\nand since we were all off on camp at the end of february, you wouldnt have been able to make a new character and try and overtake anyways, if dado was out of the way.\r\n\r\nnow, since you\'re choosing to debate my win, let\'s discuss it.\r\n\r\nthe only reason i won first month, was simply because i know how to adapt my strategies to game changes. if rizen says \"you will die for murdering people from now on\", and you go ahead and kill someone, then it\'s your own fault you were taken out by the mob.\r\n\r\nas i recall, i tried to let you win still, though, because i felt your effort over the month deserved the win moreso than mine. \r\n\r\ndont you remember? you attacked me when i was bare-handed (28 combat), and i still killed you (in self-defense, but the fatc that you had full polymer and .50 makes me wonder about your character)\r\n\r\nand about your 4 day effort;\r\n\r\ni wouldnt call your only legitimate ranking on that survivors list anything to be proud of -- considering the only other person playing sotf v1 at the time was dinsdale.\r\n\r\n*mock appluase*\r\ncongratulations ivor, you beat dins! wooh!','2001-06-04 08:26:05');
