INSERT INTO messages VALUES (1121,1121,3,0,1,'Rizen','OOC: Clans in SotF','On the dE site we\'ll be reinstating the clans system. So we thought it might be cool to create a sudo clans system for SotF. Here\'s the idea:\r\n\r\n1) We\'d use the bigger clans of the past to create the sudo clans for SotF. For instance, wraiths, null, family, alphaprime, etc.\r\n\r\n2) You\'d choose which clan you\'d want to belong to at character creation.\r\n\r\n3) You couldn\'t steal from or attack anyone in your clan.\r\n\r\n4) Each clan would have a special ability. For instance, alphaPrime could not be PK\'d. The Family could not be punished for murder. Etc. I think you get the picture.\r\n\r\nWe have these needs of you:\r\n\r\n1) Help us determine all of the important clans of the past. (We only need about 5-10, but list whatever you feel is important.) We need to know why you think the clan deserves consideration. what made that clan stand out?\r\n\r\n2) Help us determine what special abilities that you\'d like to see.\r\n\r\n3) Help us assign those special abilities to each clan. (Remember, each clan only gets one.)\r\n\r\n\r\nclans under consideration so far:\r\n\r\nAlphaPrime - for being the playtest clan\r\nThe Family - for being the first in crime\r\nThe Wraiths - for being the biggest military\r\n(what was that pro-mutant clan?)\r\n\r\nabilities under consideration so far:\r\nimmunity to PK\r\nimmunity to city governments related to murder\r\nimmunity to city governments related to theft\r\nlots of extra cash at start\r\nbetter armor and weapons at start\r\nbetter skills at start\r\nthe skill of choice is super high at start\r\nimmunity to city governments related to mutation\r\nimmunity to city governments related to guns\r\nsome immunity to poison (through toxic conditioning)\r\nsome immunity to radiation (through genetic screening)\r\n','2001-06-08 10:14:24');
