INSERT INTO messages VALUES (1123,1121,3,1121,203,'CrashAndBurn','Ohh','EXCELLENT idea!  Me like me like \r\n\r\nBUT... If you can get in a clan at character creation, then why would anyone want to go solo?  I think that  there sould also be a negitive or maybe some way to make it so you had to be invited into the clan. ei... everyone starts solo and then after say 2000 turns and if you are in the right town Clan X can invite you and if you join THEN you get their bonus.\r\n\r\nAs for the clans: I liked my clan dEad Men Walking, although we didn\'t make a big showing we had a cool name :)\r\n\r\nI like all the abilities but the higher starting skill of choice.  Because if someone knows about it can use combat and then have a \'friend\' drop some nice weapons for them and they have a good chance to be over powerful!\r\n\r\nThat\'s all I got for now, I will reply again after I thing it over.','2001-06-08 11:40:16');
