INSERT INTO messages VALUES (1135,1133,1,1133,1,'Rizen','order of operations','1) each player attacks/defends simultaneously. the one with the better combat roll will be the winner of that round of combat. (chance for broken weapon)\r\n\r\n2) damage is processed against the loser\'s armor. (chance for broken armor)\r\n\r\n3) remaining damage is processed against the loser\'s health.\r\n\r\n4) if they\'re both still alive, the next round of combat begins. this repeats for 4 rounds of combat.','2001-06-08 15:33:45');
