INSERT INTO messages VALUES (1177,1121,3,1172,15,'Fradam','what says fradam','okay, i think most of us here got so excited by the idea, we were trying to resserruct not only the name, but also the old system of sorts relating to clans.\r\n\r\n\r\nim good with what all you say\r\n\r\nmy amended suggestions\r\n\r\n<li>Alphaprime -- no attacks/thieves on them till the attacker/thief passes 6k turns\r\n\r\n<li>Null -- Half the amount of skill points required to go up in senses (this should benefit their character thruoughts its existence, by having a ridiculously high senses skill)\r\n\r\n<li>Family -- immunity to theft+murder punishments\r\n\r\n<li>Wraiths -- 2/3 amount of skill points required to go up in levels for combat. i think half the amount (as done with null and senses), <i>might</i> be too powerful, but it\'s at your discretion rizen.\r\n\r\n<li>FDP -- i honestly think we should forgo this one unless somebody can find one of the original members (even it is only TOFKAB), but if they do, then a flat 50 shielding base might be the ticket (or something along those lines)','2001-06-10 17:57:42');
