INSERT INTO messages VALUES (1569,1569,3,0,6,'Kurtillius','Hmm... ((PLEASE READ THIS))','<font color=\"pink\">Kurt pulls out a small folder, with hundreds of loose papers, and rests it on the table before him.</font>\r\n\r\n\"People, I have recently been taking down notes on an adventure that me and my fellow Null members are about to embark upon. It seems incredibly interesting, and I would wonder if any of you would be interested?\"\r\n\r\nOOC-\r\n\r\n<b>TIME FOR SOME SHAMELESS SELF-PROMOTION!</b>\r\n\r\nAll right, I just wanted to start this in character.\r\n\r\nOver the last week, I\'ve been working on a campaign for me to play. My original intent was to just write a little \'Saturday Afternoon\' plot, but the date kept getting pushed back, and ideas started pounding their way into my head... anyway, this campaign, in all modesty, is turning out to be Godlike. I mean, if you guys think that my OTHER campaigns were even REMOTELY interesting, let me assure you that this campaign is much better. I know it\'s not exactly Rizen-calibre or anything (if anything could possibly be!) but I think you guys would enjoy it with your players (assuming any of you play dE anymore.)\r\n\r\nI would normally be content to just post this under my CAMPAIGNS section when I\'m done, but I really want you guys to see this, critique it, and give my suggestions and opinions on it. I am not done (Maybe about a third, or half of the way) but I have the groundwork laid out for the rest, and I am making good progress. I would really like you guys to see this, and hopefully play through it.\r\n\r\nIf you would be interested in getting a copy when I am finished, please post on the board under this thread, or e-mail me at Kurtillius@metacrawler.com . \r\n\r\nRizen, I know you\'ve liked my work in the past, and this is really, much, much better than it, so I\'d really like you, more than anyone else to see this! Could I e-mail you a copy when I\'m done? Because you know I only live to please you!\r\n\r\nAnother side note- if you\'re a fan of subplots, or \'sidequests\', I\'m also putting alot of them in here, and trying to make the \'alot\' and \'ALOT\'. If you have any suggestions please E-MAIL ME at the address as listed above (Dont\' post ideas here, you\'d give it away for other potential players.)\r\n\r\nSo, please, if you\'re even remotely interested, let me know. Thanks for your time.','2001-06-28 00:08:36');
