INSERT INTO messages VALUES (1601,1601,3,0,1,'Rizen','Up For Discussion','We\'re considering removing all references to how many turns each feature uses on the pages. We\'re considering this to reduce clutter, and because it\'s completely unnecessary since TGC is moving SotF toward a pay-to-play medium.\r\n\r\nThis means that on pages where you are asked to do something for a number of turns, you\'ll be instead asked...\"Do you wish to scavenge for a short time/long time/extremely long time?\"\r\n\r\nTo be honest, we could not care less about the free-play users. We have free-play available simply to add some fodder to the mix for the pay-to-play members. \r\n\r\nWhat say you?\r\n\r\nMy vote is to remove the turns information from each page.','2001-06-28 15:15:17');
