INSERT INTO messages VALUES (1685,1685,1,0,15,'Fradam','a few clanhall-related ideas',' -- interclan warfare --\r\n\r\nokay, maybe not warfare, but perhaps we could have quests given out by a questmaster at the clanhall? these quests would relate to the clan, or other clans.\r\n\r\nfor example, one quest could be to retrieve a godsbane cloak (make up a story), or perhaps to kill one Null member\r\netc etc\r\n\r\n-- storing --\r\n\r\nperhaps, move the \"store an item\" feature present at ab26\'s government house, to each clan\'s clanhall?\r\n\r\nthis would make a lot more sense, sicne clans such as the Santione\'s probably wouldnt trust an institute of the law (the court house), when we\'ve got clanhalls\r\n\r\n -- greater allowance of amenities --\r\n\r\nperhaps not this month, when theres a tonne of them at bd18 (btw, why is there another alphaprime one??), which is a huge city, but next month, if we have clanhalls in average joe schmo towns, the following could be an idea;\r\n\r\nallowing a mini set of amenities at the clanhall. when i say this, i merely mean extending the current range (which would appear to be trade depot), to include market items (so that food and pelts could be traded)\r\n\r\nit could also be an idea to include a doctor, and library. it would make sense that a clan would have a physician on the grouns somewhere, but im  little edgy on the library. maybe just allow fyth clanhalls to have the library.\r\n\r\nany future for these ideas rizen?\r\n','2001-06-30 02:20:32');
