INSERT INTO messages VALUES (1757,1749,2,1756,6,'Kurtillius','\"Aargh!\"','<font color=\"black\">Kurt\'s charging swing at Fradam is disrupted by Bishop\'s attack. Kurt quickly changes the running swing into a diving soumersalt, spinning over the attack at his legs, and hitting the ground and rolling, well past his target, Fradam.</font>\r\n\r\n\"0o0oh! Bishop still has it!\"\r\n\r\n<font color=\"black\">Kurt regains his feet, and spins to face Bishop, brandishing the long stool leg with both hands.</font>\r\n\r\n\"Well, I guess Fradam owes you one, now. Mind you, I think Fradam can take care of himself. But while you have my attention...\"\r\n\r\n<font color=\"black\">Kurt steps in a brings his weapon in a wide horizontal sweep, forcing Bishop back. Kurt slowly edges towards Ring, where he stands by the Null booth.</font>\r\n\r\n\"Uh.. Ring, as much as you want to get drunk and all, I think the vodka can wait. You kind of started something that needs finishing here...\"\r\n\r\n<font color=\"black\">Kurt keeps the leg levelled in front of him, waiting for someone to make the next move, not trusting Dinsdale to be able to keep his grip on Eeeeegor.</font>','2001-07-03 02:08:49');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (1758,1749,2,1757,11,'Eeeegor','*Ragh!!!!*','<i>Eeeegor attempts to struggle out of Dinsdale\'s grip, failing.  He then doubles over, grasping at a bottle on his belt, with his teeth... he manages to get the bottle, and picks it up with his mouth, letting the contents go down his throat....</i>\r\n\r\n\"Ahhh..... that\'s something to awaken the Demon in you...\" OOC - Corny line ahoy!\r\n\r\n<i>Eeeegor is quite for a few seconds, then his eyes go up, with a red tinge in them.  With a roar Eeeegor tears himself free on Dinsdale\'s grip, throwing him down onto the ground</i>\r\n\r\n\"Rite, let\'s do it! Strength through alliance!\"\r\n\r\n<i>Eeeegor runs at Ringleader, stomping on Dindsale as he goes past, and ignoring his buddy Kurt ;)</i>','2001-07-03 04:26:13');
