INSERT INTO messages VALUES (1786,1749,2,1783,11,'Eeeegor','What will that do?!?!','\n --- (Edited at Wed Jul  4 01:49:48 2001) --- \n\n\"You think that MORE poison in my bloodstream will make much difference? HAH!\"\r\n\r\n<i>Eeeegor turns from scorning Dinsdale, and jumps at Ringleader, comes soaring through the air at him, and crashes into him, ripping Ring\'s new inventions away from him as he goes.  Eeeegor quickly gets up at stomps on them very hard, sending little pieces skittering across the floor</i>\r\n\r\n\"Quidnunc, we need something to help Fradam and Bishop out, quick!\"','2001-07-04 01:46:58');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (1787,1749,2,1783,10,'Bishop','*fumbling around...','Bishop reaches into the bottom pocket of his trenchcoat adn pulls out a misty vial. It is the serum that Doctor Valarkin gave him in return for loaning the principal to fund the expedition.  He throws similar vials to his allies.\r\n\"Who would wanna be anywhere else?\"  Bishop reaches behind his waist with both hands and flings them back into view sending his coat tails flying.  \"normally I wouldnt waste my ammo on you scum, but now you made me mad...  sharpshoot this\"  Its only now the Nullsters see Bishop\'s trademark Glocks.  He sprays a volley of fire into Null booth emptying two clips.  Bishop throws the guns towards Eeeegor, \"If you\'d be so kind\" he winks and in the one motion leaps towards the Null booth brandishing his trusty longsword, cleaving deadly strokes in the air.\r\n\r\nOOC:  this is what we were missin...','2001-07-04 01:51:22');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (1788,1749,2,1787,15,'Fradam','*applys the serum*','*Fradam\'s eyes roll back as the serum takes effect. He shakes out the kinks in his muscles that had begun to lock up, and his hands dart within his clothing. From assorted places, he picks up crusty old.. cookies*\r\n\r\n*As Fradam drops and turns around to face Racer, he lets lose a cookie, and it collides with the dagger, which goes skittering under a table.*\r\n\r\n\"Ally with what, my dear?\"\r\n\r\n*Laughs maniacally, and runs away from the centre of the tavern, at a low croush, so that Ring can\'t see him with the Null peashooter*','2001-07-04 01:58:45');
