INSERT INTO messages VALUES (1793,1749,2,1788,6,'Kurtillius','\"Phew...\"','<font color=\"black\">Kurt is suddenly very glad he went to cower in the corner. He slowly uncurls from his fetal position in the corner, and looks up to the mayhem going on around him.</font>\r\n\r\n\"Uh... Fradam, you wanna come hide and cringe with me until all the guns and pointy things go away?\"\r\n\r\n<font color=\"black\">Kurt flips a table onto its side, and pulls it into the corner, legs sticking outward, making a semi-usable barricade.</font>\r\n\r\n\"Uhm... I\'ll just guard this corner here.\"\r\n\r\n<font color=\"black\">Kurt ducks back behind the table, clutching his stool leg.</font>','2001-07-04 02:45:43');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (1794,1749,2,1788,572,'NULL-RingLeadeR','*Pushes Button Under Table*','*Ring sees Bishop running at him and pushes a button under the table.. within seconds the table tips on its side and there is an opening in the floor where it was*\r\n\r\n*Ring watches cheerfully as Bishop Goes flying into the basement aka.. the dark pit*\r\n\r\n\"Hey Bishop.. Hope you have matches ya bastard!\"\r\n\r\n*Evil Grin*\r\n\r\n\"Dins, Racer.. Get EEEGOR! Kurt why dont you continue to beat on Fraddam.. First one to send em to the grave gets dinner on ole\' Ring.\"','2001-07-04 02:45:59');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (1795,1749,2,1794,11,'Eeeegor','*Eeeegor catches the glocks...','\n --- (Edited at Wed Jul  4 03:00:36 2001) --- \n\n<i>And they go whirling on his fingers as he spins around, quickly slipping a pair of magazines into them, and finishing his whirling to have a straight aim at both Racer and Dinsdale with one glock on either</i>\r\n\r\n\"One motion, one little motion, and you two get blown into oblivion.  Trust me boys, i know how to use these things\"\r\n\r\n<i>Eeeegor motions to his State Championship trophies for shotgun, and pistol</i> OOC - which i do actually have, btw</i>\r\n\r\n\"Hey Ring, you should know better than to send inferiors to deal with one of the golden oldies.  Never send boys to do a man\'s job\"\r\n\r\nIn memory of Wiccan - Mess with the best, die like the rest','2001-07-04 02:58:51');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (1796,1749,2,1795,6,'Kurtillius','\"Eep.\"','\"Normally, I\'d be compelled to rescue the Boytoys, but those ARE glocks...\"\r\n\r\n<font color=\"black\">Kurt pulls a small pouch out of his back pocket, and lights a match on the table he\'s ducked behind.</font>\r\n\r\n\"Ah... homemade flash powder...\"\r\n\r\n<font color=\"black\">Kurt sits down, placing his back against his table barricade. He drops the match into the pouch and tosses it over his shoulder, into the middle of the tavern. It goes off in midair, a loud bang rocking through the tavern and a bright flash filling everyone\'s eyes with a near-blinding light, momentarily stopping the battle and getting everone\'s attention.</font>\r\n\r\n\"Hey, everybody! Why don\'t we pull back a sec, and let Bishop and Ringleader go at it, man to man, leader on leader!\"\r\n\r\n<font color=\"black\">Kurt hops over the table and walks over to Eeeeegor.</font>\r\n\r\n\"May I?\"\r\n\r\n<font color=\"black\">Kurt takes one of the pistols from Eeeegor, and levels it at Dinsdale\'s foot.</font>\r\n\r\n\"I <i>said</i> back off so the leaders can fight, Dinsdale! That\'s an order!\"\r\n\r\n<font color=\"black\">Kurt fires the glock point blank into Dinsdale\'s foot. The bullet continues through and into the floor.</font>\r\n\r\n\"Sorry about that. Go get a rag. Now, move these tables aside for the big fight!\"\r\n\r\n<font color=\"black\">Kurt tosses the gun back to Eeeegor, and begins clearing the area.</font>','2001-07-04 03:10:05');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (1797,1749,2,1796,11,'Eeeegor','*Levels the guns again...*','\n --- (Edited at Wed Jul  4 03:13:53 2001) --- \n\n<i>At Racer and the now wounded Dinsdale, waiting for them to step down before Eeeegor complies</i>\r\n\r\n\"Fradam, get some pails of water, and towels for the big fight, please =)\"\r\n\r\nOOC - I allowed Kurt to control my character for that post =)','2001-07-04 03:11:42');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (1798,1749,2,1797,15,'Fradam','*walks on over to the bar*','\"Hey Quid, can you ask Sheila to bring us around some pails and water for the fight?\"\r\n\r\n*walks over to the still-injured Dins.*\r\n\r\n\"Do you mind?\"\r\n\r\n*with a deft movement under his sleeve, there\'s a blade in one hand, and Fradam cuts one end of Dins\' belt apart and yanks it out with the other.*\r\n\r\n\"Thought not..\"\r\n\r\n*Turns over to the hole*\r\n\r\n\"YO, Bishop, I\'m gonna lower down some.. rope... when you\'re ready..\"','2001-07-04 03:28:47');
