INSERT INTO messages VALUES (2026,2025,3,2025,5,'Racer X','Rules, as I know them.','Being the newest edition before yourself, I\'m still sorta picking everything up as I go along, but here they are as I know them:\r\n\r\n1. Respect is shown to everyone.\r\n\r\n2. In bar fights, no pulling a \'Fradam,\' as it\'s known. That\'s when you control someone elses character without their consent.\r\nExample: <font color=\"white\">*Racer walks up to Slender. Slender runs around like gopher and kills himself.*</font>\r\n\r\n3. Keep the SotF talk to  minimum in Quid. If you want to discuss it, boards are set up outside, as you know.\r\n\r\n4. Try to make your post \"In character.\" Just like you have through the bar fights so far. But if you feel the need to go out of your character, the subject of your post should begin with \'OOC\' (Out Of Character).\r\n\r\nIf anyone can think of anything else, please post it, cause I\'d like to know, too.','2001-07-08 15:46:42');
