INSERT INTO messages VALUES (2028,2028,5,0,5,'Racer X','ATTENTION ALL IDIOTS','And by idiots, I mean members of AlphPrime.\r\nBy joining AlphaPrime, you\'re depriving yourself of the first objective of this game. To survive.\r\nThe only way you can be killed is by creature attacks and thiefs.\r\nOkay, so my point is, don\'t join it. It\'s contradicting the entire objective of the game. It also makes it boring, and pointless.','2001-07-08 16:25:49');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (2029,2025,3,2027,447,'Slender','So...','Is it \"disrespectful\" to haul out a .45 and blow a fellow Quidder away in the game?  Or hork all their stuff and leave \'em to starve?  \r\n\r\nCuz I\'ll have to buy a 2nd character if it is...','2001-07-08 16:49:25');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (2030,2028,5,2028,447,'Slender','Idiot?','Think, dude.\r\n\r\nLet\'s assume, for a sec, that this month I\'m trying to \"win\", not smear Racer X all over the map like I did last month...\r\n\r\n1) The way to \"win\" is to survive the most moves. \r\n\r\n2) There\'s no advantage gained by killing other characters, and an extremely large disadvantage to being in a position where I can be killed. \r\n\r\nThe math is simple. \r\n\r\nI\'m not gonna step outside my room at Bottle & Barrel until I see someone coming close to my number of moves. \r\n\r\n\"It\'s contradicting the entire objective of the game?\"\r\n\r\nFrom a analytical perspective, it looks to me like the \"objective\" of the game is to survive the most number of moves.  \r\n\r\nWhat needs to change is the game, not my play.  Last month I was playing around.  And kicking butt.  Punk butt.\r\n\r\nThis month I\'m trying to \"win\", even though it\'s dead boring.  Next month, I\'ll probably get back to kicking ass. \r\n\r\nProbably.\r\n\r\nIf the spider webs don\'t get too thick first...','2001-07-08 17:05:49');
