INSERT INTO messages VALUES (2067,2053,1,2053,5,'Racer X','Strategy and a suggestion','My strategy:\r\n\r\n1) Start with decent skills\r\n2)Don\'t join AlphaPrime, and make your self liked by people.(Take that, Slender!)\r\n3)Sit, and scavenge. (There are spots that are best for doing this, but I\'ll keep that between Dins, Slender, and myself.)\r\n\r\n\r\nNow, my suggestion.\r\nTake away the inventory limit, and bring back worth to the ranks. It doesn\'t have to be part of it, but you have to admit, if you have more stuff, you\'re going to be more powerful. It\'s as simple as that. Turns would still be a big part of the ranks. Say something like -  -  - worth + (turns x5) = rank\r\n\r\nI proposed this before, and I never did see why it wouldn\'t work!','2001-07-08 21:11:00');
