INSERT INTO messages VALUES (2072,2053,1,2067,15,'Fradam','Can we say, Bishop the ATM?','Don\'t you remember how raughted that system was Racer?\r\n\r\nThe inventory limit is probably one of the best things rizen ahs implemented, becuase it brings ALL players to sthe same playing field, so it\'s not dead boring for us PTP Players.\r\n\r\nSlender -- my age old strategy required far less time than yours, but it came from a time clans didn\'t exist, there was no such thing as \"unlimited turns\" (well, there was, if you knew how to manipulate the casinos), and the lynch mob wasnt around, and in addition, there was no \"newbie status\"\r\n\r\nThe strategy went as follows;\r\n\r\n1. Create a character\r\n2. Kill every other character\r\n\r\nPretty simple, eh? =)\r\n\r\nProbably won\'t work now too well now, but I\'m sure rizen will find a way to get around this boring strategy, and I\'m quite sure it will surround AlphaPrime.\r\n\r\nrizen -- perhaps we can change the bonus from AlphaPrime? Keep the Invulnerability from PK-ing, but only allow characters who pass, say 10,000 turns from being able to do so to AlphaPrime members.','2001-07-08 21:28:33');
