INSERT INTO messages VALUES (2257,1749,2,2242,447,'Slender','* In a bad way *','\n --- (Edited at Wed Jul 11 01:53:23 2001) --- \n\n --- (Edited at Wed Jul 11 01:47:59 2001) --- \r\n\r\n --- (Edited at Wed Jul 11 01:46:49 2001) --- \r\n\r\nMeanwhile...\r\n\r\n* Spattered with a disgusting mixture of his own blood and Kurt\'s last meal, Slender sprawls on the floor, gasping helplessly for breath.  He is definately having trouble breathing, much less listening to Kurt\'s generous offer.*\r\n \r\n\r\n\"Aahhhhhuuuuuuuuuuhhhh!\"\r\n\r\n* He rocks back and forth for a few moments. Then, slowly, in a sequence of moves so clearly _practiced_ as to seem automated, Slender digs a stimpack from a pocket inside his leather coat and injects it into his tooth-marked arm. *\r\n\r\n\"Much... better....\"\r\n\r\n* Yet again, Slender struggles to his feet.  Seeing Kurt turn his back, he starts a running leap.  As he springs into motion, his left foot slips on a bit of half-digested cat meat.  Arms windmilling, he crashes back to the floor, injuring his head a fourth time in as many minutes * ','2001-07-11 01:44:39');
