INSERT INTO messages VALUES (2265,2120,3,2244,15,'Fradam','i say','renown is given for\r\n\r\n<li> quests --> flat rate amount\r\n\r\n<li> monsters --> decrease exponentially, and only for the most powerful of creatures (im thinking that list we had up.. paunchers, angry roots, and terrors). however, i dont think this should work on a player by player basis.\r\n\r\ni think it should exist across the board for all characters, but that the level of renown for it slowly increases over time (because the idea of killing somthing that powerful becomes more and more .. exciting again)\r\n\r\n<li>other players --> portion of their renown.\r\n\r\n<li>rads (just the eerie glow one) --> something really small\r\n\r\n<li>random events --> again, as above, something really small (remember how we used to catch a town\'s murdered, and they would give us 500 $tandards, when we had like 600k+ $tandards?)\r\n\r\nalso, i occasionally get those events where a woman comes running up to me, telling me that Dins has raped her, or a man comes up to me, saying Racer took all their money --> tiny bonus to renown, perhaps? (these all just ideas on which random events for renown)\r\n\r\n<li>clans --> i believe being known as a member of a certain clan should feed you a tincy amount of renown, based upon how much renown as a whole the clan is gaining (why am i sensing a return of cotm?)\r\n\r\nhmm... i cant think of anything else just yet... if i do, ill edit it in..','2001-07-11 03:23:24');
