INSERT INTO messages VALUES (2542,2520,3,2528,1,'Rizen','no','\n --- (Edited at Mon Jul 16 16:22:05 2001) --- \n\ni know that in real life the richest people are almost always famous, but with the way wealth comes and goes in SotF i\'m afraid there would be a lot of unnessary calculations on the back-end.\r\n\r\ni would not judge whether the story was worthy of renown, rather your skill would judge your story. \r\n\r\ni\'ve said time and time again that worth is of no value in sotf. therefore it shall not appear on the ranks. i may put it on interesting tidbits at some juncture for the \"highest\" worth, but only for that. i don\'t want pk\'s and theives to go after peeps just cuz they have a few trinkets...and that\'s the only purpose for putting worth in the rankings.\r\n\r\nif you are a pickpocket you never really know if your going to get a wallet full of moths or dollar bills....so it should be in sotf.','2001-07-16 16:21:41');
