INSERT INTO messages VALUES (2679,2679,1,0,5,'Racer X','HOW TO GAIN RENOWN','Okay, this is for all you who don\'t know how to gain renown. Renown will get ALOT higher in the ranks.\r\n\r\nFirst of all, go kill at least one of every animal in the game. ((Don\'t worry about vim dawgs, shriekers, crimson terrors, dropbears, devil (angry) roots, or danbury paunchers quite yet.))\r\n\r\nThe animals are:\r\nwild boar, goat, rabbit, squirrel, rat, fox, goose, snake, deer, wolverine, hawk, wolf, bear(Bears have a combat of 15, so make sure you can kill them).\r\n\r\nOnce you have killed all the animals, go to a tavern in any town you can find, and click on the \'gossip\' boards, and write a story about your adventures in killing the animals. One at a time.\r\nFor each animal, you will get 1 renown. And you may have to gossip in more than one place to get the renown.\r\n\r\nAfter you\'re done with the animals, stay in the tavern, and click on \'talk to the bartender.\'\r\nHe will give you quests sometimes (you\'ll have to talk to him more than once), and when you complete those, you gossip about how you completed them, and will gain renown. AGain, you will most likely have to gossip in more than one town to gain the renown.\r\n\r\nThere. Now you\'re on your way.\r\n\r\n<b>NOTE TO READER:</b> This is ALOT easier to do if you take $2 and pay to play.\r\n','2001-07-19 11:18:51');
