INSERT INTO messages VALUES (2788,2788,3,0,15,'Fradam','Motion: Tavern Personalites','Taverns atm are somewhat moreso boring than I believe they should be.\r\n\r\nI believe that there ought to be people other than the bartender to speak with.\r\n\r\nWith each of these people you would be able to gossip with and because of their reflected personality/trade, the gossip could result in:\r\n\r\n<li>Being spread (gain renown)\r\n<li>Stop it from being spread\r\n<li>Slapped to the face (a point of health lost)\r\n<li>Kicked about (a few points of health lost)\r\n<li>Get a few standards and applause\r\n\r\nThe idea behind the violence, is that some personalities might not approve of the stories you\'re telling.\r\n\r\nFor example, gossiping about sleeping with a lady (if that was a quest) to the lady\'s husband, could entail you getting punched up a bit.\r\n\r\nJust general talking with them will get the short gossip bits related to their personality/trade.. buying them a drink, completeing a few quests etc, will allow you to read the longer gossip stories.\r\n\r\nIn addition, each of these persons could hand out quests too, thus allowing more freedom in the types of quests given, and allowing it to be developed somewhat more, with less sketchy connections given (i.e. rather than saying -- \"see that guy over there? he needs blah blah\" that guy himself could be talking to you and asking for blah blah)\r\n\r\nWhat do you all think?','2001-07-23 00:20:44');
