INSERT INTO messages VALUES (2936,2837,2,2935,15,'Fradam','*half-turns*','*Fradam turns around and begins walking back towards Rafael, with a gleam in his eye. His pace is constant, bar the few moments he stops and wrrenches free another barstool leg.*\r\n\r\n\"Correction, I merely joined another clan <b>in addition</b> to the Santiones. Yeah, I did make a hit on you... but I wouldn\'t say that\'s reason enough to leave a person... I mean, if you currently look at who you\'re siding with, they\'re far more involved with these things that you\'re professing to be against than I ever was...\"\r\n\r\n*Fradam watches him roll on the ground, waiting till he\'s on his back, then throws the stool leg into Rafael\'s groin.*\r\n\r\n\"Some people..\"\r\n\r\n*returns to the mass melee*','2001-07-26 02:09:52');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (2937,2837,2,2936,19,'Dinsdale','<font color=\"green\">*Dins...','\n --- (Edited at Thu Jul 26 03:01:47 2001) --- \n\n<font color=\"green\">gets up, shaken up pretty badly from fradams stomping. He turns toward the Null table, and grabs a bottle of Demon Scotch. He pours out a little of the demon scotch onto the floor. \r\n\r\nHe then grabs the salt shaker, and pours it all into the bottle of scotch. He proceeds to take the bottle over to the bar, and whispers to Quidnunc*\r\n\r\n</font>\"mumble mumble.....vinegar....mumble\"\r\n\r\n\r\n<font color=\"green\">*He pours the vinegar into the bottle, and hears the mixture start to bubble. He puts a cork on, tipping it back and forth to mix it together a bit. \r\n\r\nHeads back to the Null booth, and pulls out 5 small glass vials. He pours the bottle\'s contents into the vials, and stores 4 of them on the inside pocket of his leather jacket. The other one, he throws at fradam, hitting him squarely in the forehead, the contents spilling out and leaking into fradams eyes.\r\n</font>\"That\'ll show you. HAve fun with your eyes. You cheap bastard.\"\r\n\r\n<font color=\"green\">Sits in the Null booth, and sips what\'s left in the bottle of Scotch, then immediately, goes into convulsions while lying in the booth. \r\n\r\n</font>\"It burns! It BURRRRRRRRNS!!!!!\r\n\r\n','2001-07-26 03:00:00');
