INSERT INTO messages VALUES (2985,2822,3,2976,6,'Kurtillius','Fradam, Read this.','\n --- (Edited at Sat Jul 28 23:35:55 2001) --- \n\nYou don\'t listen, do you? You don\'t lose anything about your character. You just start again in another town, 100% complete, with just another kill for the other team\'s war kill count. That\'s all. You didn\'t even take the time to understand what I was saying before ATTACKING it, you dumb fuck. You just disagreed because I can never be right, and this is why I\'ve always fucking hated you so much.\r\n\r\nSo, in summary-\r\n\r\nUntil you understand, don\'t cut it down. Remember how I said you ALWAYS have to have the final word? Well, you proved me right again, munchkin bastard.\r\n\r\nI just thought that having this, which perhaps you understand now-\r\n\r\nYou can kill and be killed without consequences, it only affects the war kills count. The winning clan gets renown. That\'s IT. You don\'t LOSE anything like you were saying Fradam! You were spitting on me AGAIN for something I DIDN\'T DO OR SAY, YOU MEANIE. \r\n\r\nBut you don\'t care. You just like to argue. But do you understand what I mean NOW?!?!?!','2001-07-28 23:30:50');
