INSERT INTO messages VALUES (3007,2837,2,3004,15,'Fradam','\"Blah\"','\"Ooof!\"\r\n\r\n*Fradam lands outside with a thud, and after grabbig his breath back, he storms back into the Tavern, slowly nursing the side he landed on as he makes his way to face Dinsdale*\r\n\r\n\"Excuse me Dins!? Who had the armoured car??! Who had them strange crossbow thingies!? Who brought in vials of liquid that scaled the eyes!? Who is it that chooses to ignore their injuries\"!? I SPIT at you Dinsdale!\"\r\n\r\n*spits at Dins*\r\n\r\n*makes the motion of turning around and walking away, but instead, turns, and runs straight into Dins, and lashes out in blind fury with both fists, striking all of Dins upper torso and face.. after a few punches however, he feels sore from the exertions and increasing pains in his side, and gets off Dins*\r\n\r\n\"What an idiot.\"\r\n\r\n*walks over to Quid slowly and whispers something about possible cracked ribs*','2001-07-29 19:23:39');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (3008,2921,1,3001,15,'Fradam','also','though i disagree with this idea on realism, here\'s my thoughts;\r\n\r\nimplement the COD idea, so that it aint free (or buy stamps from the market, perhaps?)\r\n\r\nalso, allow it so that you can send an item to another person thru the mail system, but if it\'s a trade-type agreement between 2 players, that the items doens\'t get delivered until the other player has at least put out the desired item on their end of the table\r\n\r\nthis ensures that direct trading of items occurs simultaenously\r\n\r\nif thats not implemented, tehre\'ll be a sense of distrust with regard to this if you\'re trading across different time zones..','2001-07-29 19:27:57');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (3009,3009,3,0,5,'Racer X','OOC: Inac-freakin-tivity','Is it just me, or has Slender been relatively (and by relatively, I mean completely)inactive in the past 20 days? \r\n\r\nOr is that just me, Rizen?\r\n\r\nUrrrgghhh...This is shaping up to be just the way I didn\'t want it to be. The way Fradam said it would. Damn you, Fraddy! I blame this squarely on you, and Ivor, for some reason.\r\n\r\nMaybe it\'s the whole Aussie thing..=) Crazy Aussie\'s...\r\n\r\nAnyways.. Speaking of being bored...\r\n((IC now..)\r\n\r\n*Walks over to Dins and punches him in the groin*\r\n\r\n\"Quid! I\'ll have some water! And get Ugly here some ice!\"\r\n\r\n((OOC again!!))\r\n\r\nI know this could have been in bar brawl, or the second part of it at least, but I really didn\'t wanna change message boards just to punch Dins. I mean, it\'s a pretty basic thing to do around here. I don\'t think Quid would mind.','2001-07-29 22:31:58');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (3010,2921,1,3008,5,'Racer X','Stamps','Stamps, I think, are a great idea, aside from the fact that Fradam suggested it.\r\n\r\nI propose making a COD-like charge to recieve a package, and stamps in order to send one. Also, there should be certain things you can\'t send through the mail. ((IE: I don\'t think you could really send a monkey in a box or something. It just wouldn\'t work.))\r\n\r\nAnd yes, having it set so that trading is simultaneous is good. No one gets screwed over that way.\r\n\r\nI second this motion, Colonel Stacy.(Fradam)\r\n\r\n','2001-07-29 22:38:21');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (3011,2837,2,3007,19,'Dinsdale','\"Ugh\"','\n --- (Edited at Mon Jul 30 00:33:24 2001) --- \n\n*Dins stumbles back into the Null table, adrenaline rush depleted. He begins to feel the pain in his side again, the pains that his adrenaline temporarily replaced. He also feels a black eye coming on. He sits down in the Null booth.*\r\n\r\n\"Ah, hell. I\'ve had enough of this for now.\"\r\n\r\n*Takes off Racers shirt, and fashions it into bandages for his side.*\r\n\r\nOOC-You say that I used the crossbow. Wrong. Yes, i was a passenger in the armoured car, but did the armoured car ever hurt you? No. So consider us Almost even. We would be even if not for you using a blade weapon that would realistically have a 70% chance of killing me.','2001-07-30 00:31:31');
