INSERT INTO messages VALUES (3098,3098,3,0,1,'Rizen','Motion: Changing Freeplay','I think everyone agrees that this game needs a hell of a lot more active players if it\'s going to be interesting. To do that we need to change freeplay. This change needs to have the following effects:\r\n\r\n<li>More active players.\r\n<li>Incentives for free players to upgrade to ptp.\r\n<li>Heavily weighted advantage to ptp players.\r\n\r\nRight now PTP players have a huge advantage in unlimited turns vs not.\r\n\r\nHere\'s what I suggest:\r\n\r\nEITHER:\r\n\r\n<li>give freeplayers 5000 starting turns instead of 2000, but keep newbie status at 1800.\r\n\r\nOR:\r\n\r\n<li>give freeplayers unlimited turns\r\n<li>remove freeplay access to geneticists, doctors, trade depots, and blacksmiths.\r\n\r\nI need to know your thoughts. Keep in mind that in the end, SotF is a part of TGC business. In order to continue providing SotF as a service, it eventually needs to make money. As long as it makes money, I\'ll continue it as a service, and I\'ll continue developing it. Therefore if you like SotF, it is in your best interest to help me make SotF succeed financially.\r\n\r\nMy questions to you are these:\r\n\r\n<li> Which of my suggestions above do you think is better to get more people playing?\r\n\r\n<li> Do you have any other suggestions to get more people playing?\r\n\r\n<li> Do you think that my suggestions above will incite more people into PTP?\r\n\r\n<li> Do you have any suggestions to get more people into PTP?\r\n','2001-08-01 09:34:48');
