INSERT INTO messages VALUES (3100,3098,3,3098,19,'Dinsdale','yup. I agree.','\n --- (Edited at Wed Aug  1 13:13:47 2001) --- \n\nNEWBIE RULES-5000 turns. And maybe give them access to the clans system. It does make the game better, and could help provide incentive for newbies to PTP. If you gave them unlimited turns, that would be good too, but you can\'t cut them off from all those shops. That would make the game boring, and also, some people wouldn\'t need those places. They\'d steal it off someone or kill someone, then they\'re God, and they aren\'t even PTP-ing. Another idea is: unlimited turns, inability to steal from or attack PTP players, inability to use geneticist, and no trade depots.\r\n\r\nTo attract more people to SotF in the first place, first off, TELL YOUR FRIENDS, EVERYONE!! Like you said Riz, if everyone got all there friends to at least try the game, there would be many more PTPers. Also, those banners really seemed to bring alot of players in. MAybe it was just me, but there were alot of players in SotF1. And we had the banners up back then. MY favourite idea would be the unlimited turns, no attack/steal for non PTP\'s. What do you guys think?\r\n\r\n','2001-08-01 13:02:32');
