INSERT INTO messages VALUES (3125,3098,3,3120,5,'Racer \"The Dumb One\" X','CLAN-FREAKING-WARS','You all know it\'s a good idea. And let\'s face it, special skills and privileges are all well and good, but if you can only put them to use against... no one, then they\'re not doing much. I mean, EVERY PTP player (except maybe one or two) is a Quidder, and has abdicated basically from playing the game by claiming allegiance to all other Quidders (except Dins.. but that\'s just Dins.), and the only way to restore any kind of difficulty, and entertainment to the game is through all out war, with a few changes, which have already been mentioned.\r\n\r\nI know you all like playing the game, or you wouldn\'t have paid for it. So let yourselves play, damnit. Don\'t just sit there and stack up turns and not touch anyone, except occasionally killing or stealing from the odd newbie.\r\n\r\nYou know you want this. Don\'t resist the urge!\r\n\r\nPS: Think about it. You could legally kill <b>me</b>!!!\r\n\r\n((If there\'s any spelling or grammar errors, it\'s because I typed this quickly. And it\'s midnight, and I\'m not going over it. Also, any words that are used in the wrong place are also under that excuse!))','2001-08-02 01:01:06');
