INSERT INTO messages VALUES (3462,3394,5,3460,969,'shlominus','you make me laugh','1) about having to earn trust. correct, nobody in his right mind will trust YOU now. the implication of this fact will be explained a little further below.\r\n\r\n2) if you think the plan sucks, thats your opinion. i think it would have worked last month. i am not sure, but if i remember correctly 80 renown(and i still think i would have managed to get that much :P) would have been enough to gain a top 5 spot, even with newbie moves.\r\n\r\n3) how a plan can suck and be the entire point of the game at the same time, thats a paradox only you understand. of course it is NOT the entire point of the game. if you ptp you could (and most likely would) use different tactics. as you played this game longer than i have, you could have tried this completly obvious tactic, maybe even succeded, as it would be surprising the first time it is used. but thats for people who are able to plan of course. which doesnt include you, as your plans seem to consist of being killed in any way by anyone at any time.\r\n\r\n4) survival without trust. of course people you can trust add to your chances of survival, not reduce them. as noone will trust you now, your chances went down by betraying me. i didnt think you had any reason to betray me, thats why i told you what i planned to do. i thought, as we were both freeplayers trying to make the top5, it would make the race a little more even, as it became obvious very quickly, that wouldnt stand a chance otherwise. i still dont understand your reasons for posting my message to you and i would be interested to know why you did it.\r\n\r\ni didnt really expect an apology or anything, but your reply was exactly the way i imagined it,almost to the letter. we dont know much about each other, apart from seeing how the other one plays the game. that you would insult me, even though i am superior to you by far, in the only issue we have available to compare, leads me to believe that you are an insecure and immature individual, that needs to make himself appear smart and tough by trying to make fun of someone and lecturing him about trust. grow up, develop self-confidence and respect for others. you never know, maybe someday you will turn into a nice guy.','2001-08-15 08:04:41');
