INSERT INTO messages VALUES (3466,3394,5,3462,5,'Racer X','Here\'s an idea..','\n --- (Edited at Wed Aug 15 13:55:02 2001) --- \n\nYou want HIM to get self confidence? He\'s not the one quitting the game. So in other words, shut the hell up.\r\n\r\nAnd secondly, your whole idea about trust is backwards. Chemical Halo said it right. In a world like this, there\'s no one you can trust. Unless you\'re in Quid(which you\'re not), but even in Quid there are some shady characters...\r\n\r\nAlso, I\'m pretty sure, that by \"Your plan sucks,\" he meant that, if there\'s any other plan, it must suck. I mean, if you get someone with 80 renown, and someone with zero. PTP or not, that person is gonna beat you.\r\n\r\nIf I remember right, you said that you were gone after hitting 50 renown. So go. And take your trust with you.','2001-08-15 13:54:39');
