INSERT INTO messages VALUES (3470,3394,5,3466,969,'shlominus','nice idea... not','if you had a little more knowledge of psychology you would have understood what i meant about his self confidence. if you think i lack it because i quit you most likely havent read any of my posts. and telling me to shut up proves that your manners are lacking, as do some of your other posts.\r\n\r\nwhat is wrong about my idea about trust? i just found out that halo doesnt deserve any. having people to trust is always better than being alone. if you cant grasp that, too bad. you must lead a sorry life if you feel that way. or you watched madmax too often.\r\n\r\nand i know that there a \"shady\" characters among the quidders. you know that i know, remember?\r\n\r\nfunny how you explicitly state that i am not in quid. lol, how could i be, i play this game for 3 weeks now and without ptp. how could i ever be a quidder? the same principle about self confidence applies here, you try to put me down to lift yourself up (im in quid, you are not). therefore, the same advice, grow up.\r\n\r\n>Also, I\'m pretty sure, that by \"Your plan >sucks,\" he meant that, if there\'s any other >plan, it must suck. I mean, if you get someone >with 80 renown, and someone with zero. PTP or >not, that person is gonna beat you. \r\n\r\num, what do you mean to tell me with that paragraph?\r\n\r\nyou remember wrong. i didnt say id be gone after 50, i said i would stop playing and had 50 already, 54 to be precise. but after reading dinsdales post about 65 being hard to get , i will play this month to the end, so i can find out if i can reach my 80. and maybe i will even fins people to trust. i already know that you are not to be trusted, remember? ;)\r\n\r\n','2001-08-15 16:20:52');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (3471,3394,5,3470,5,'Racer X','Manners?','You want to talk about manners? How about you, telling everyone they need self confidence? I mean, who are you to tell ANYONE what they need? If anything, you need it. I mean, telling me that <b>I</b> put <b>YOU</b> down to up my own self confidence. It\'s almost laughable.\r\n\r\nSpeaking of laughable... You. You\'re attempts to reach 80 renown are actually sort of funny. You act as though it\'s some amazing feat that no one else could ever accomplish. And as though it\'s something that should be noted by everyone. The truth is, I couldn\'t care less about the amount of renown you pile up. The only thing I care about is that people like you, who think they can just do what they wish with everything (IE: telling them what they \'need\'), leave and don\'t come back.\r\n\r\nI say good riddance.','2001-08-15 17:27:51');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (3472,3394,5,3471,969,'shlominus','lol, i agree with you','actually telling people their weaknesses can be considered bad manners. but thats beside the point, of course. i explained how i came to my conclusions while you just strike back \"if anything, you need it\". any reasons why? why dont you share them with me. as for who i am to tell anone what they need, i didnt do that. i just wrote what i think. people like you could never accept any criticism anyway. it was my impression that most people today have a little knowledge of basic psychological mechanisms. you obviously dont.\r\n\r\nexplain why you did write that part about me not being a quidder. i would like to know what the point of that sentence was. maybe i am wrong, but i doubt it.\r\n\r\nif you think it is laughable, feel free to do so. your arguments make it hard not to question your intellectual capacity. sorry, bad manners again, but i couldnt help it. you seem to forget that i dont ptp. i dont know if there have been free players that have managed to get that much renown, as i have been here only 3 weeks. but as dinsdale(a player you hopefully respect) posted, reaching 65 would be an accomplishment. \r\n\r\nhow do you reach the conclusion that i want everyone to take note of it? the whole thing came up cause halo couldnt keep his mouth shut for reasons still unknown. it seems your arguments are a bit weak, you just seem to make stuff up to. i will try to do it, as a personal goal, if any other freeplayer has done it before or will in the future he has my respect. i think i am doing a nice job so far. if my skill at playing amuses you, so be it. i have no problem with that.\r\n\r\nas i just explained, i did not and do not care what others think about me, that was just one of your made up points. and hey, you even manage to make one bogus argument out of your first one. if you care about my renown doesnt mean anything to me, but your problem with \"people like me, who think they can do what they wish with everything\" is really interesting. how do you make that stuff up? lol, thats hilarious, real comedy. i am eagerly awaiting your next outburst.','2001-08-15 17:55:30');
