INSERT INTO messages VALUES (3648,3648,3,0,5,'Racer X','<b>MOTION: NEWBIE WINNINGS</b>','\n --- (Edited at Thu Aug 23 13:50:39 2001) --- \n\nI wanna get this over with, because it\'s just simply pissing me off.\r\nEver since renown was put in place, and people realized they could sit high in the ranks without coming out of their newbiehood, no one spends over 1800 turns. And frankly, it\'s making the game ALOT less fun. I mean, everyday when I come on here, there\'s absolutely <i>nothing</i> to do.\r\n\r\nI propose, officially, that you <b>cannot</b> place in the top 5 of you are still in your newbie status.','2001-08-23 13:50:01');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (3649,3649,4,0,447,'Slender','Ahem.  God bug, apparently.','Rads are one thing, but this is ridiculous.\r\n\r\nI\'ll be back in a few weeks and hopefully this mess will be sorted out.\r\n\r\n\r\nbeast lore 711 Dinsdale \r\ncombat 795 Dinsdale \r\ndomestics 700 Dinsdale \r\nfirst aid 714 Dinsdale \r\nhaggle 695 Dinsdale \r\nhork 702 Dinsdale \r\nnavigate 682 Dinsdale \r\nsenses 723 Dinsdale \r\nstealth 714 Dinsdale \r\ntracking 713 Dinsdale \r\ntroubadour 703 Dinsdale \r\n','2001-08-23 16:43:15');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (3650,3648,3,3648,13,'tera','wrong motion','I think that you have the wrong motion then. What you are proposing is not necessarily going to make people be non-newbies. I mean, it\'s a real bonus to come back to the game after 12 hours and see you still have a character. Maybe now that everyone has had achance to see what renown is like, it needs to be tweaked.','2001-08-23 18:02:36');
