INSERT INTO messages VALUES (3652,3648,3,3650,5,'Racer X','Know what else is a bonus?','Leaving the game, knowing there\'s no possible way anyone can do anything to you, and only playing when you know it\'s safe, and when no one else is. Knowing that you can safely spend 1799, do a few things that need to be done, and then kill your character off (not necessarily by way of the \'commit suicide\' button), and do that over and over and over until you have everything done that needs to be done. That\'s also a bonus.\r\n\r\nWhat I\'m trying to say is, that right now, as it stands, all you get from paying to play, is a geneticist, and a trade depot. Oh, and the clans.\r\n\r\nWe need something that gives people incentive to NOT be a newbie. Or at least have the ability to steal from newbies. Because they way it is right now, is you\'re completely invincible to other players as a newbie. And yes, I\'m aware newbie status is for people to get a feel for the game without being maliciously attacked, but for there has to be some sort of happy-medium for all the players who have a clue as to what they\'re doing.\r\n\r\nAnyone have any other ideas?','2001-08-23 18:53:15');
