INSERT INTO messages VALUES (3692,3687,5,3690,1393,'Dalak','LOL','\n --- (Edited at Wed Aug 29 07:09:57 2001) --- \n\nRacer,\r\nYou really should work for the powers that be. You would make a great spin doctor. I love how you took part of a long conversation, in which you were quite rude and demanding, and used it to spin what actually happened. You started off the conversation by demanding that I \"answer your fucking questions\". That isn\'t rude? You then continued to blather on and whine about the fact that i was killing you. The game is survival, staying alive at all costs. I didn\'t realize their were unwritten rules of conduct. Would you mind posting them for my consideration please. \r\n\r\nIn addition, I won\'t take any of this seriously as Racer advised me........Racer X shouted, \"Message boards?? Do you actually take those seriously? Give your head a\r\n                                     shake man.. Things aren\'t the way you see them.\"','2001-08-29 07:06:57');
