INSERT INTO messages VALUES (3702,3687,5,3700,5,'Racer X','Contradictions','\n --- (Edited at Thu Aug 30 00:14:16 2001) --- \n\n8/29 10:44 AM Dalak shouted, \"Nice job Racer. Taking a portion of a conversation and using it to try and discredit someone is the oldest smear campaign trick in the book. Eliminates pesky issues like context. As I said before, you are a consummate idiot.\"\r\n\r\nHe called me that once before, too. I\'m wondering if the \'consummate idiot\' could do what I did. Have the sense to post Dalak\'s contradictions, in a scheme that can only unravel itself in time.\r\n\r\nI\'m wondering if it isn\'t him, that is the \'consummate idiot\'... I mean, you\'d think he might be able to come up with something new every now and then, instead of \'fucker\' and \'consummate idiot\'.\r\n\r\nIt puzzles me when people are like this. I\'m predicting severe childhood trauma, with a rough break-up to cap it off.\r\n\r\nPS: If anyone wants the entire conversation (Well, what Dalak said to me. That\'s all I have.), then I\'d be more than happy to post it.','2001-08-30 00:06:16');
