INSERT INTO messages VALUES (3704,3687,5,3702,1393,'Dalak','LOL More','Racer,\r\nI find it quite amusing that you are here in the message boards slamming me to the other players. It seems to be a continuation of the whining you did to me in private. I wonder why it is that you feel you have to tell everyone that you are upset. Did I hurt your feelings? In terms of not answering you even though I was obviously online, I was answering the phone. Sorry if you don\'t come out as one of my higher priorities.\r\n\r\n Go ahead and post the entire message if you want. I didn\'t bother to cut it out and save it because you were making no sense anyway. It does make sense that you would save it though. Just the sort of thing an attention seeking juvenile would do. Oh look how Dalak called me rude! Mommy!! Racer just drop it. Don\'t let anger cloud your judgement. I wouldn\'t want you to make a mistake or something. Give it a rest.','2001-08-30 07:45:51');
