INSERT INTO messages VALUES (3713,3706,4,3707,1075,'Raptor','That Sucks','\n --- (Edited at Fri Aug 31 07:33:00 2001) --- \n\nYet another player who will never pay to play this game. It\'s not that i have a problem with not posting the notification. My problem is that you changed the fundamentals of the game the day before it ended. I was playing to win within a certain set of understood rules. Minor changes I have no problem with. But major changes in the rules should not be done the day before the end. \r\n\r\nRizen, you want people to pay to play and yet you change things and set things up to discourage people to do so. The game is only a month long. Why not wait until September to make a major rules change?\r\n\r\nWhy is it that dying does not change your renown, but suiciding does. If I attack a pauncher, that is the same as suiciding. And yet I lose nothing. You say that I only got top 68 through suicide, and you are right. But you set the game up to allow people to succeed that way. It is not my fault that I played smart. Very Disheartening.','2001-08-31 07:26:33');
