INSERT INTO messages VALUES (3717,3706,4,3713,1,'Rizen','i\'m sorry','i\'m sorry that you are disheartened, but i\'m not sorry for changing things. the features page and several other areas say that the games changes a lot.\r\n\r\ni\'m also sorry that you will never be a pay to play player, but to be honest, 9 out of 10 people who play SotF will never PTP. i suspect you were in that 9 before i changed the rules.\r\n\r\nthe rule change was mandated by Quidnunc, not by me. Quidnunc Parliament makes all the decisions as to rule changes in SotF. the rule change was made to stop people from abusing the \"commit suicide\" option in the game.\r\n\r\nas i said, i\'m sorry that you\'re upset, but there\'s nothing i can or will do about that.','2001-08-31 13:20:34');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (3718,3715,1,3715,1,'Rizen','looking into that','we\'re already looking in to building a 3D game based on deadEarth, but it won\'t be survival of the fittest. it will be a whole new type of game. if we do it the new game will likely be called \"Clan Wars\" and it will be a 3D RPG deathmatch system. it will likely have the 3D tactical elements of Swat 3 or Rainbow Six, but it will also have some role-playing elements and character and clan development.\r\n\r\nas i said earlier though, we are not sure whether we\'ll be developing this game or not, nor are we sure what a potential release date might be. we have already begun purchasing and testing various 3D game dev suites, but we\'re unsure that we could afford to pay all of the programmers and artists necessary to pull off a game of that magnitude.','2001-08-31 13:25:35');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (3719,3715,1,3718,1,'Rizen','one more note','if we do this game there will be no free version what-so-ever.','2001-08-31 13:27:22');
