INSERT INTO messages VALUES (4041,4026,1,4040,5,'Racer X','Right.','You\'re right about the hork. Hork is your slight of hand skill, stealing.\r\n\r\nTroubador is your story telling skill. You use it in taverns, and tell stories on the gossip boards about deeds you have done.\r\nDeeds include:\r\nKilling animals while hunting\r\nKilling other players\r\nSurviving random attacks\r\nCompleting quests given by the bartender\r\n\r\nYou\'ll get a deed for each thing you do. (Example: Killing a deer is a deed. Killing Dojie is a deed.)\r\n\r\nYou go into taverns, and brag about it, and you get renown.\r\nRenown multiplies the amount of turns you\'ve spent, and increases your chances at winning by alot. Paying to play does the same thing, and I suggest you do that. It\'s much easier to win, and really cheap, too.','2001-10-03 21:15:25');
