INSERT INTO messages VALUES (4406,4367,1,4404,969,'shlominus','if i may...','i would suggest 2 more changes.\r\n\r\n1)skills should rise quicker. for example, when you kill 100 snakes(a quest) and work the hides you should notice some singificant increase in domestic skill. thats not the case now. my combat skill has gone up 1% and i have the most kills. practice should be more imprtant than getting good rads.\r\n2)a party system would be great. a couple of people(maybe 3 or 4 max.) could \"gang up\" and gain benefits when they are in the same square.','2001-11-26 15:22:07');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (4407,4367,1,4397,2615,'Gualdhar','Thats really stupid to me','Really, the entire idea of deadEarth and SOTF is to SURVIVE.  If you don\'t have the common sence not to attack a vim dog or angry root when you have a knife as a weapon, you will learn from it (although it may cause some frustration).  Same thing with attacking big people.  Learned that lesson with a little help :)  By the way Scholominus, i still owe you one for that move.','2001-11-26 16:17:27');
INSERT INTO messages VALUES (4408,4367,1,4367,2615,'Gualdhar','My answer is a','Also, make it a little easier for people to get to them.  For instance, all my renown is from killing things.  you can only get so much renown for that, and I can\'t find any other quests.','2001-11-26 16:19:15');
