INSERT INTO messages VALUES (4450,4450,1,0,1075,'Raptor','Changes','\n --- (Edited at Mon Dec  3 10:52:28 2001) --- \n\nRizen,\r\nI\'ve only had a bit of time to check the new changes. In general they seem very good.\r\nGame play is much faster.\r\nI must say that the 1000 turn cap adds a new dynamic.\r\nIf you are carrying more than about 250 items it is almost impossible to scavenge it all back and stay under the cap.\r\nAdds an interesting dynamic and will hopefully keep the hoarding of items to a minimum.\r\nAt least they will be available most of the time,\r\nif you can rob or kill for them.\r\nWell done.\r\n\r\nEdit: I noticed that there is new rewards for winning. Are these on top of the credits for winning?','2001-12-03 10:43:16');
