INSERT INTO messages VALUES (4511,4511,1,0,5,'Racer X','Suggestion','I don\'t know why I didn\'t think of this before, but I did now.\r\n\r\nA memory skill. \r\nIf you have a bad memory, your skill deteriorates over time. If you have a high memory skill, your skills deteriorate much slower, and to a lesser extent.\r\n\r\nThe skill could be advanced in casinos (which would also make a use of that elusive gambling skill we don\'t have) by playing games of memory and ones that make you think. Not just slot machines.\r\n\r\nWhat does everyone think? Anything to add?','2001-12-05 20:49:06');
