INSERT INTO messages VALUES (4909,4909,1,0,1,'Rizen','SotF Lives!','As most of you know SotF was scheduled to be discontinued after this month. For financial reasons we still must discontinue it, but we wanted to give one last hoorah to our loyal fans. We\'re doing that in two ways.\r\n\r\n1) Sometime in March we\'ll be releasing the SotF source code as open source software. This means that if anyone has a server, and wants to set up their own SotF site they can do so using our code. The best part is that you\'ll then be able to modify it to your liking.\r\n\r\n2) We\'ve decided to continue SotF3 for one more month (March) and we\'re going to open all the Pay To Play functionality to every player so that we can get some real Clan warfare and competition going, and go out with a BANG! Get all your friends, family, and enemies out to play for this last month and let us finish with a bang rather than a whisper.\r\n\r\nThanks to all the SotF players for keeping SotF alive and kicking for its 16 month existence.','2002-02-26 22:50:57');
