INSERT INTO quests VALUES (1,'There is a scientist who lives not far from here that is in search of a special ingredient for a formula he\'s working on. He needs one vile of crimson terror dust to complete the experiement. He\'s willing to pay hansomely for the vile. Will you bring it to me?',164,1,1,3000,'find and return','Terror Dust Experiment');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (2,'A book collector that I know is looking for a copy of <i>Uncle Tom\'s Cabin</i>. If you can seek out this book for me, I\'ll reward you with a rare and valuable gem. Will you find this book?',89,1,24,1,'find and return','Rare Uncle Tom');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (3,'As you know the winter months on deadEarth are unbearably cold. I need to gather 3 more vim dawg pelts to complete my winter coat. If you can bring me the remaining pelts I\'ll trade you an entire box of .50 ammunition for them. Will you bring me the pelts?',153,3,107,25,'find and return','Special Winter Coat');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (4,'A traveling trader stopped by recently and told me a tale of a magnificent gemstone. It was a radiation gem, but not of ordinary size. He claimed it was double the size of an ordinary rad gem. If you can find this gem, I\'ll trade my Geiger counter for it. Will you trade if you find it?',26,1,79,1,'find and return','Extraordinary Gem');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (5,'A legend has been traveling through gambling circles for as long as I can remember. The legend tells of magical gem dice. It is said that the man who gambles using these dice cannot lose. If the game requires that you roll low, then you shall. If it requires that you roll high, then you shall. <p>I have discovered that the legend is true. I have learned the names of the cities where the dice are hidden. If you can locate these dice, I shall reward you with the grandest protection in this cursed wasteland, a radiation suit. Will you find these dice for me?',180,5,13,1,'spawn in city','Magical Dice');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (6,'An old friend of mine is coming to the area soon and wants to do some hunting while she\'s here. Do you think you could round up a map detailing the best hunting spots? I\'ll be happy pay you hansomely for your efforts. What do you say?',181,1,1,1100,'find and return','Hunter\'s Visit');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (8,'I have a very sensitive package that I need delivered to a fellow bartender in another city. If you\'re willing to take it to him, he\'ll give you some very nice armor when you arrive. Will you transport the package?',193,1,11,1,'give and deliver','Sensitive Package');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (14,'Hey, do you like my necklace?  Ive been making it from animal teeth. All I need now is the teeth of a drop bear and it will be finished.  I cant go and get them myself; Im stuck here while the boss is out of town.  Im willing to pay handsomely; Ill give you this large radiation gem here.  Can you find me a pair of drop bear teeth and bring them back to me?',195,2,26,1,'find and return','Toothed Necklace');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (15,'Oi, yeah you, come ere!  Do you know of the drop bears?  Ive eard rumours about giant monsters that drop from the trees on to unsuspecting travelers and paralyze em before eating them alive.  My mate over there in the corner has worked out how to use their poison while hunting.  He used to crush the meat and extract the poison, which he would dips onto his arrows.  The thing is, hes been lost the use of his legs after a drop bear attack.  All he does is make the arrows now.  If you can bring back 11 drop bear steaks Im sure he will give you his old copy of <I> Animals and Habitats</I>.  Are you good enough to bring em back for my old mate?',194,11,51,1,'find and return','Poison Hunter');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (11,'I\'m gonna build me a pool in the back yard, but see the problem is, the mayor here has strict guidelines on safety regulations...which I know nothing about. I hear there is books about that sort of stuff that could help. Could you find me one?',49,1,149,100,'find and return','Pool Rules');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (12,'My daughter\'s birthday is coming up, and she wants me to buy \"The cat in the hat\". The problem is i can\'t leave the bar unattended. Would you get me one?',91,1,79,1,'find and return','The Birthday');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (13,'I have been working on a set of snakeskin boots to give out at my squaredancing club, but I ran out of skins. I\'ll need about 50 more to complete. Could you find them for me?',159,50,183,10,'find and return','Dancin\' Boots');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (16,'Stranger, you look like you have traveled this land.  Have you by chance come across a jar of vegemite?  My daughter has just been bitten by a drop bear and its her only hope.  Im desperate, Ill give you whatever you want, Ill even give you this old .44 handgun if you like.  Im beggin you stranger, can you find me a jar of vegemite?',196,1,127,1,'find and return','Jar of Vegiwho?');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (17,'What can I get ya?  Whats that? Youre looking for work?  Well I aint got nothing for ya but I know my good friend Doctor Valarkin needs some help. He is working on a serum to combat drop bear venom and needs 6 more steaks for his research.  Hes told me that whoever brings back the steaks for him will get a bottle of his antidote.  He works in secret so if you bring me the 6 drop bear steaks I will get you your anti-toxin.  Are you up to it?\r\n \r\n',194,6,183,1,'find and return','Dropbear Cure');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (18,'Me wife has been bugging me for a bracelet made from dropbear teeth. Her birthday is coming up real soon and I\'d like to give her that bracelet for her special day.\r\n<p>\r\nI\'ve also paid a tracker to scout out some of the dropbears\' favorite hang outs. You won\'t have to kill the bears, just find and collect the teeth from dead dropbears.\r\n<p>\r\nIf you could bring back six dropbear teeth, I\'d be willing to trade you my GPS for your efforts. Are you willing to trade?',195,6,80,1,'spawn in wilderness','Deadly Bracelet');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (19,'Hey You! Yeah you ugly,  see that man sitting in the corner?  He is the Wraith\'s best marksman.  People call him Scope.  He needs a stash of bullets and I told him that I would find them for him.  He needs 40 .35 bullets. If you find him he told me he would give you his old copy of <i>\"US Army FM 21-76\"</i>.  Will you do it?',109,40,52,1,'find and return','Sharp Shooter');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (20,'My good friend Godot has lost his favourite kazoo. He hasn\'t been the same since. Be a sport and go buy him one.  If you do I\'ll give you a bar tab.  Oh let\'s say ten drinks? Can you do that for us?',65,1,150,10,'find and return','Musical Bar Tab');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (21,'See that shady character in the corner?  He is a Null operative. The word is that his higher-ups have ordered him to infiltrate the Wraiths\' ranks.  He needs a pair of Wraith fatigues but doesn\'t want ot blow his cover by asking around.  Can I trust you to bring a pair back here?  He promised a scavenging map to whoever returned here first with a pair.  Will you get the fatigues?',197,1,182,1,'find and return','Secret Null');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (22,'Hey! Don\'t stare at him.  He will rip your arms off.  He was once a well renowned adventurer.  He had it all; riches, fame, women, now he has been hideously disfigured by radiation.  He refuses to leave the drakness of the corner without a godsbane cloak.  If you go and get it for him he will give you his old Type III vest as it doesnt fit him anymore.  Will you get the cloak and bring it back?',204,1,74,1,'spawn in city','Cloak of Shame');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (23,'Kids huh!? My son has played hockey for our local team.  Now he has decided that he wants to play football.  Problem is that all the other kids are way bigger and I wont let him play without a helmet.  If you can find me a football helmet I will swap it for his hockey pads.',143,1,23,1,'find and return','Kids and Sports');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (24,'Psst... see that fine lookin\' lady over there?  Her name\'s Matilda.  The fat balding guy is called Jeb.  Jeb wants a bath and Matilda wants to give it to him.  She has run out of soap though and needs someone to go and get some more.  If you can bring back three cakes of soap she will give you her old copy of the Kama Sutra *wink*.  Hurry though Jeb has a short temper... will you get the soap?',61,3,92,1,'find and return','Bathhouse Babe');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (25,'Are you a dog lover? My friend Bryn, he\'s a bartender too you know, is also a dog breeder.  He sent me this letter the other week asking if I would send him my golden retriever to mate with his.  If you do this for him I\'m sure he will let you pick a dog from his litters.  His favourite breed is the pitbull.  Will you take my dog?',42,1,147,1,'give and deliver','Making Puppies!');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (26,'My friend is a geologist.  He is studying the effects of radiation gems on animal biology.  He told me that if anyone can find ten large radiation gems and bring them back he will give them his old geiger counter.  Will you get those gems for him?',26,10,79,1,'spawn in wilderness','Geological Biologist');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (27,'I\'m so tired.  My wife has the worst gas problem in the wastelands.  If I\'m gonna get any sleep i need to find some charcoal tablets. No one around here seems to sell them though.  If you could bring me a bottle of 10 tablets I will gladly give you my copy of \"Art of the Trade\",  it\'s a small price to pay for a good night\'s sleep.  Will you help me stranger?',184,10,55,1,'find and return','Fartknocker');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (28,'Hey you man... help me out, i need a lighter, I\'m addicted to the lung lollies, the durries, the fags, the cancer sticks, the smokes, man i need a cigarette.  I\'ll give you anything *twitch* get me a lighter and I\'ll give you... what\'s this?  \"The Cat in the Hat\" - here if you get me a lighter you can have this.  Can you get me a lighter?',39,1,91,1,'find and return','The Addict');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (29,'I remember a movie from long, long ago. It was called Fight Club.  These guys made soap from human fat.  I want to give that a go.  Do you think you could find me 4 human steaks so that I can get the fat from them and turn it into soap. I wont ask questions and I will give you the soap when I\'ve made it.  What do you say? ',104,4,61,2,'find and return','Dubious Soap');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (30,'The mayor was in here the other day. He put that poster up over there. - Whats that? - You cant read?  Pity, I\'ll read it for you. *ahem*  It says: \"Attention good citizens, the rat problem is out of control.  He or she who first brings 100 rat pelts to the back of this bar will receive a radiation suit courtesy of the local government.\"\r\nCan you handle that?',158,100,13,1,'find and return','Pied Piper');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (31,'Hey you, see that guy smacking that other guy around the head?  Thats Tyler Durgen.  He makes soap among other things.  What he really needs though is two sets of brass knuckles.  Im sure he would give you some of his soap in return.  Can you get those brass knuckles?',101,2,61,6,'find and return','Tyler Makes Soap');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (32,'Hey, have a look at this... Its notes on how to make a football.  Lucky thing that lady passed them on to me.  My son has just started playing football.  I want to try my hand at making a few balls for the club.  If you could get about 5 pigskins and bring them back I will give you a handy little bar-tab.',186,5,150,10,'find and return','Piggy Football');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (33,'Hey you, there is a new clan in the area.  They call themselves \"The New Ones\"  Every night they come into town and cause trouble, thinkin\' they own the place.  You can pick \'em by the shawls they wear.  The mayor is sick of their shinanigans... they stole his last hairpiece the other night.  He is <i>really</i> pissed off - he even set a bounty.  300 $tandards for every shawl you can get.  It doesnt matter how you do it, just bring em back here and I\'ll fix you up.  If you want to collect the bounty you\'ll need five shawls.  Up to it?',113,5,1,300,'find and return','Gnubee Hunter');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (34,'Hi! You want more? Well how about this great set of steak knives?  Hardy and ready for your next dinner party or hunting expedition. *blinks* Sorry, I was talking like my cousin Tim there for a moment.  Do you think you could deliver this set of steak knives to my nephew?  He runs a bar not too far from here.  I\'m sure you will be rewarded for your efforts.  Can you do this for me?',112,12,48,2,'give and deliver','Demtel Man');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (35,'Do you remember the days before the war?  Every Sunday we would have hot pie and ice cream after a roast dinner.  Mmmm i can still taste the Berry pies my ma used to bake.  I\'d be much obliged if you would hunt one down for me.  I\'ll let you eat all you can here, but dont be expecting much of that pie. *smiles*  Will you get me some pie like ma used to make?',102,2,149,5,'find and return','Pie.');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (36,'Hey you! Do you know where I can get my hands on a pair of Null Overalls?  I got this book ere a while back.. \"talk dirty and Influence People\"  I thought it was about something else, but it turns out its not. Now I just want to run away and join Null.  If you could get me a pair of overals you could have this book \'ere. Deal?',202,1,54,1,'find and return','Null Wannabe..');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (37,'Hey you.. I have a regular in here, his name is heero something.  He was telling me how he \"read\" a good book the other day.  He wanted to know if I knew where to find another one.  Perhaps you could find him something at his level.  I know you can find a copy of the Cat in the Hat around.  He said he is willing to pay handsomely.',91,1,1,600,'spawn in city','story time for heero');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (38,'Good to see you. I\'d been hoping you\'d come around. I have a job for you if you\'re interested. I want to build a suit of armor out of pangolin scales. I know how to do this, but it requires a lot of scales and I just don\'t have the time to be running around looking for pangolins. If you bring back enough scales for two suits, I\'ll make you one too. I think around 200 scales should do nicely.',206,200,210,1,'find and return','Pangolin Armor');
INSERT INTO quests VALUES (39,'Hey I\'m not just a bartender you know, Im the road safety officer of this town.  Some rogues keep horking our only stop sign.  There is a bounty of 2500 $standards if you can bring it back.',22,1,1,2500,'find and return','Road Safety');
